title: Walk In Your Heavenly Father's Shoes
itunes:title: Walk In Your Heavenly Father's Shoes
description:
Whatever you’re facing today, know that God has all the strength you need. You don’t have to shrink back in fear or give up. When you grab hold of His strength, He will take you to places you’ve never dreamed.Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love. To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
